---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="As-Built Company — Millimeter-Accurate 3D Scanning Across California"
  description="Survey-grade 3D laser scanning and as-built documentation across California. Delivered as CAD, Revit, point clouds, and virtual tours."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="eyebrow">3D Laser Scanning · As-Built Documentation</div>
      <h1>Millimeter-accurate as-builts <span class="accent">across California.</span></h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Survey-grade 3D laser scanning and 360&deg; capture for architects, contractors, and property owners.
        We deliver the drawings, models, and walkthroughs your project actually needs.
      </p>
      <div class="actions">
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn">Get a Quote <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
        <a href="/services/" class="btn btn-outline-light">Explore Services</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Trust strip: the one place equipment + accuracy lives -->
  <div class="trust-strip-wrapper">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="trust-strip-content">
        <span class="strip-label">Trusted by Design &amp; Construction Teams</span>
        <span class="trust-item"><span class="trust-icon">◆</span> Leica BLK2GO</span>
        <span class="trust-item"><span class="trust-icon">◉</span> Insta360 Pro</span>
        <span class="trust-item"><span class="trust-icon">⚡</span> 2&ndash;4 mm Accuracy</span>
        <span class="trust-item"><span class="trust-icon">◎</span> California-Wide</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Stat block: only unique numbers, no equipment/accuracy duplication -->
  <section class="stat-block-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="stat-grid">
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="number">24 hr</span>
          <span class="label">Quote response<br />for new project inquiries</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="number">3&ndash;7 days</span>
          <span class="label">Typical turnaround<br />from on-site to deliverable</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="number">10+</span>
          <span class="label">Output formats<br />DWG, DXF, PDF, RVT, RCP,<br />RCS, E57, LAS, PTS, OBJ, IFC</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="number">100%</span>
          <span class="label">In-house processing<br />no third-party handoffs</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What we do — short service descriptions without equipment repeats -->
  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-title-centered">
        <span class="eyebrow">What We Do</span>
        <h2>Capture. Document. Visualize.</h2>
        <p>End-to-end as-built services scoped to your project, your team, and your timeline.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-3">
        <div class="icon-card">
          <div class="icon">◧</div>
          <h3>3D Laser Scanning</h3>
          <p>High-density point clouds of interiors, exteriors, and full sites &mdash; survey-grade and ready for downstream work.</p>
          <a href="/services/" class="link-arrow">Learn more <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
        </div>
        <div class="icon-card">
          <div class="icon">▤</div>
          <h3>As-Built Drawings</h3>
          <p>Floor plans, elevations, sections, and details drawn from scan data &mdash; CAD and Revit, ready to design from.</p>
          <a href="/services/" class="link-arrow">Learn more <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
        </div>
        <div class="icon-card">
          <div class="icon">◉</div>
          <h3>360&deg; Virtual Tours</h3>
          <p>Interactive walkthroughs your team can navigate in any browser. Share a site without flying anyone out.</p>
          <a href="/services/" class="link-arrow">Learn more <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
        </div>
        <div class="icon-card">
          <div class="icon">▦</div>
          <h3>BIM &amp; 3D Modeling</h3>
          <p>LOD 200&ndash;400 Revit and Rhino models built from registered scan data &mdash; for coordination or design development.</p>
          <a href="/services/" class="link-arrow">Learn more <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
        </div>
        <div class="icon-card">
          <div class="icon">⊞</div>
          <h3>Construction Documentation</h3>
          <p>Recurring site capture for milestone documentation, dispute mitigation, and remote stakeholder updates.</p>
          <a href="/services/" class="link-arrow">Learn more <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
        </div>
        <div class="icon-card">
          <div class="icon">⌂</div>
          <h3>Real Estate Floor Plans</h3>
          <p>Dimensioned floor plans for listings, lease drawings, and property records &mdash; typically delivered in 48 hours.</p>
          <a href="/services/" class="link-arrow">Learn more <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 3-step process — no equipment names, no "days/weeks" repeat -->
  <section class="section-surface">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-title-centered">
        <span class="eyebrow">Our Process</span>
        <h2>From site visit to deliverable.</h2>
        <p>A straightforward three-step workflow that fits your project schedule.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-grid">
        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="step-number">1</div>
          <h3>Scan</h3>
          <p>On-site capture coordinated around your job site. Mobile-mapping for interiors and exteriors plus 360&deg; for shareable walkthroughs &mdash; minimal disruption to active work.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="step-number">2</div>
          <h3>Process</h3>
          <p>Registration, decimation, and quality control done in-house. Point clouds tied to control where required, exported in your team&rsquo;s preferred format.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="step-number">3</div>
          <h3>Deliver</h3>
          <p>CAD drawings, Revit models, virtual tours &mdash; whatever your project needs. We stay available for revisions and follow-up scope after handoff.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Industries served -->
  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow">Industries Served</div>
          <h2>Who we work with</h2>
        </div>
        <a href="/industries/" class="link-arrow">View all industries <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-3">
        <a href="/industries/" class="industry-card">
          <div class="industry-icon">▲</div>
          <h3>Architects &amp; Design</h3>
          <p>Existing conditions for renovations, retrofits, and adaptive reuse projects.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/industries/" class="industry-card">
          <div class="industry-icon">⚒</div>
          <h3>General Contractors</h3>
          <p>Pre-construction scans, progress capture, and coordination support.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/industries/" class="industry-card">
          <div class="industry-icon">⌂</div>
          <h3>Real Estate &amp; Brokerage</h3>
          <p>Floor plans, virtual tours, and listing-ready visualizations.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/industries/" class="industry-card">
          <div class="industry-icon">◉</div>
          <h3>Insurance &amp; Forensic</h3>
          <p>Damage documentation, loss assessment, and dispute-ready records.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/industries/" class="industry-card">
          <div class="industry-icon">◇</div>
          <h3>Historic Preservation</h3>
          <p>Non-contact documentation of fragile and protected structures.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/industries/" class="industry-card">
          <div class="industry-icon">⚙</div>
          <h3>Facility Management</h3>
          <p>Accurate floor plans and as-builts for ongoing operations and planning.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonials -->
  <section class="section-surface">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-title-centered">
        <span class="eyebrow">What Clients Say</span>
        <h2>Trusted on real projects.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="testimonial-grid">
        <div class="testimonial">
          <div class="quote-mark">"</div>
          <p class="quote">As-Built Company saved us weeks of field measurement on a 12,000-square-foot renovation. The drawings came back accurate to the conditions and ready to design from.</p>
          <div class="author">
            <div class="avatar">SK</div>
            <div class="author-info">
              <span class="name">[Client Name]</span>
              <span class="role">Project Architect, [Firm Name]</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial">
          <div class="quote-mark">"</div>
          <p class="quote">Fast turnaround, clean point clouds, and a Revit model we could actually use without rework. Easiest scan vendor I&rsquo;ve worked with in California.</p>
          <div class="author">
            <div class="avatar">MR</div>
            <div class="author-info">
              <span class="name">[Client Name]</span>
              <span class="role">BIM Manager, [Firm Name]</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial">
          <div class="quote-mark">"</div>
          <p class="quote">The virtual tour they delivered let our entire team review the site from across the country. Cut a week of travel out of the project.</p>
          <div class="author">
            <div class="avatar">JT</div>
            <div class="author-info">
              <span class="name">[Client Name]</span>
              <span class="role">Senior PM, [Firm Name]</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Recent projects: real samples with floor plan thumbnails -->
  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow">Recent Projects</div>
          <h2>See our work</h2>
        </div>
        <a href="/projects/" class="link-arrow">View all projects <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-3">
        <a href="/projects/" class="card" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
          <div class="card-image has-thumb" style="cursor: pointer;">
            <img src="/images/floor-plans/costa-mesa-office.jpg" alt="Healthcare facility floor plan" loading="lazy" />
            <span class="card-badge">Commercial</span>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3>Healthcare / Outpatient Clinic</h3>
            <p>~10,000 SF outpatient medical facility &mdash; operating rooms, exam rooms, labs, and patient area.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-footer">
            <span>Costa Mesa, CA</span>
            <span class="arrow-link">See more →</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/projects/" class="card" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
          <div class="card-image has-thumb" style="cursor: pointer;">
            <img src="/images/floor-plans/laguna-hills-estate.jpg" alt="Luxury estate floor plan" loading="lazy" />
            <span class="card-badge">Residential</span>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3>Luxury Estate Floor Plan</h3>
            <p>Full existing-conditions floor plan of a Nellie Gail Ranch single-family estate.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-footer">
            <span>Laguna Hills, CA</span>
            <span class="arrow-link">See more →</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/projects/" class="card" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
          <div class="card-image has-thumb" style="cursor: pointer;">
            <img src="/images/floor-plans/laguna-hills-flex.jpg" alt="Industrial flex space floor plan" loading="lazy" />
            <span class="card-badge">Industrial</span>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3>Light Industrial Flex Space</h3>
            <p>4,962 SF warehouse + office with 16&prime;-6&Prime; clear height and 12&prime;&times;12&prime; dock doors.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-footer">
            <span>Laguna Hills, CA</span>
            <span class="arrow-link">See more →</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-surface">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-strip">
        <div class="text">
          <h3>Ready to scan?</h3>
          <p>Tell us about your project. We respond within one business day.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn">Get a Quote <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
